# 🧮 Advanced Calculator (Tkinter GUI)

A modern **Android-style calculator** built using Python and Tkinter.
This project focuses on **clean UI design, keyboard interaction, and safe mathematical operations**.

---
    
## 📸 Preview

![Calculator UI](../assets/Screenshot_00.png)

---

## ✨ Features

* 🎨 Modern dark-themed UI (inspired by Android design)
* ⌨️ Full keyboard support (Enter, Backspace, operators)
* ➕ Basic operations: Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division
* 🔄 Continuous calculations (chain operations)
* ⚠️ Error handling (division by zero, invalid input)
* 🧠 Smart number formatting (removes unnecessary `.0`)
* 🖼️ Custom app icon support

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* Python 🐍
* `tkinter` (GUI)
* `Pillow (PIL)` (for icons & images)

---

## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
# Navigate to the calculator folder
cd Calculator

# Run the app
python Calculator.py
```

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
Calculator/
├── Calculator.py
├── calculator.png   # (optional icon)
└── README.md
```

---

## ⚙️ Key Concepts Used

* Event-driven programming
* GUI layout management (Frames, Canvas, Grid)
* Input validation
* Keyboard bindings
* State management (current value, operator, reset logic)

